      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2017 Porsche Macan S in Volcano Grey Metallic. This vehicle has been a reliable daily driver and has been serviced exclusively at authorized centers; I have a comprehensive folder of all maintenance records, including the most recent 40,000-mile major service. The 3.0L V6 twin-turbo engine runs smoothly, and the PDK transmission shifts flawlessly. The interior features premium Black leather that remains supple, with only minor bolsters wear on the driver\u2019s seat. All electronics, including the Bose Surround Sound and navigation, are fully functional. Externally, the paint retains a deep gloss, though there are a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side alloy wheel. The tires were replaced last season and have approximately 75% tread remaining. This is a smoke-free, pet-free vehicle with a clean title in hand, ready for its next owner to enjoy the perfect blend of utility and performance.",
